Note that in order to generate the tests bundle for the test server,
the administrator *must* activate the 'test' module in its user
profile:

  _MODULES_		+=		test

Then, the kaneton tests can be safely compiled as shown below:

  $> cd test/tests/kaneton/
  $> make
  [...]
